  TutorialText: "Tr\u1EA3 l\u1EDDi c\xE1c c\xE2u h\u1ECFi si\xEAu \u0111\u01A1n gi\u1EA3n
    \u0111\u1EC3 v\u01B0\u1EE3t qua m\xE0n ch\u01A1i"
  TimeLimit: 60
  MaxLives: 3
  Questions:
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 1: C\xC2U L\u1EA0C B\u1ED8 WEBDEV UIT L\xC0 C\xC2U L\u1EA0C
      B\u1ED8 TR\u1EF0C THU\u1ED8C?"
    Answers:
    - "A. Khoa C\xF4ng ngh\u1EC7 ph\u1EA7n m\u1EC1m"
    - "B. Khoa Khoa h\u1ECDc & K\u1EF9 thu\u1EADt th\xF4ng tin"
    - "C. H\u1ED9i sinh vi\xEAn tr\u01B0\u1EDDng UIT"
    - "D. \u0110o\xE0n khoa tr\u01B0\u1EDDng UIT"
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 2
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 2: HTML L\xC0 T\u1EEA VI\u1EBET C\u1EE6A G\xCC?"
    Answers:
    - A. HyperText Markup Language
    - B. Hyperlinks and Text Markup Language
    - C. Home Tool Markup Language
    - D. Hyperlinking Text Management Language
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 0
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 3: TRONG CU\u1ED8C THI WEBDEV ADVENTURE, TH\xCD SINH KH\xD4NG
      \u0110\u01AF\u1EE2C S\u1EEC D\u1EE4NG N\u1EC0N T\u1EA2NG N\xC0O \u0110\u1EC2
      L\xC0M S\u1EA2N PH\u1EA8M?"
    Answers:
    - A. ReactJS
    - "B. Flutter ho\u1EB7c React Native"
    - "C. WordPress v\xE0 c\xE1c c\xF4ng c\u1EE5 no-code."
    - D. Node.js
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 2
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 4 : TRONG GIAO TH\u1EE8C HTTP, M\xC3 TR\u1EA0NG TH\xC1I
      (STATUS CODE) N\xC0O B\xC1O HI\u1EC6U R\u1EB0NG SERVER \u0110\xC3 NH\u1EACN
      \u0110\u01AF\u1EE2C Y\xCAU C\u1EA6U NH\u01AFNG KH\xD4NG T\xCCM TH\u1EA4Y T\xC0I
      NGUY\xCAN (TRANG WEB) \u0110\u01AF\u1EE2C Y\xCAU C\u1EA6U?"
    Answers:
    - A. 200
    - B. 403
    - C. 404
    - D. 500
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 2
  - QuestionText: "C\xC2U 5: T\xCAN G\u1ECCI \u0110\u1ED8I H\xCCNH XU\xC2N T\xCCNH
      NGUY\u1EC6N DO C\xC2U L\u1EA0C B\u1ED8 WEBDEV CH\u1EE6 TR\xCC L\xC0 G\xCC?"
    Answers:
    - "A. Xu\xE2n l\u1EADp tr\xECnh"
    - "B. L\u1EADp tr\xECnh Web"
    - "C. Xu\xE2n Web"
    - "D. Gu Xu\xE2n"
    CorrectAnswerIndex: 1
